description: When Parker London was late for his rent last month, James Jameson wasn't too happy that he'd have to pay his buddies share. In his opinion, if Parker wasn't paying with cash, he'd have to pay somehow! Luckily when it was time for justice to be served, we had the cameras rolling to catch the action between the two roommates. What action is that? Well, since Parker didn't have any money, but has an ass and a mouth, James thought it was only fair that Parker give up the goods to make things even! And so the two get it on!Enjoy!
title: Late Rent
